    %section.col-md-5

      :markdown
        ## All clouds are your clouds

        Most workloads are scattered between RHEV, oVirt, vSphere,
        Amazon EC2, and/or OpenStack.

        Juggle everything between providers according to your
        preferences — closer, cheaper, more performant, better
        scalability, or increased privacy — and do this automatically
        through policies you set.

        ManageIQ lets you control everything, completely, from one end
        of a virtual machine lifecycle to the other, in your browser.



      -#:markdown
        ## Configured to your needs

        Automate and deeply customise the lifecycle of your VMs;
